org.jsonurl.stream

Class JsonUrlCharSequence

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jsonurl.stream.AbstractCharIterator
      • org.jsonurl.stream.JsonUrlCharSequence
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CharSequence, CharIterator, Resource

    public class JsonUrlCharSequence
extends AbstractCharIterator
implements CharSequence
    A CharIterator that reads from a CharSequence.

    This class provides a CharIterator interface for any CharSquence, such as String. Note that the length is cached in the constructor, so don't use this class if the underlying content can change after it is constructed (e.g. a StringBuilder that you're appending to).

    Since:
    2020-11-01
    Author:
    jsonurl.org, David MacCormack
